You have dealt with many of the archer formations patrolling the perimeter around Brockbridge.
Archer formations have been spotted patrolling the perimeter around Brockbridge. They should be dealt with.
The perimeter is not as deadly as it once was, until the White Hand sends more reinforcements.
The perimeter around Brockbridge is swarming with Dunlending archers. Even an unskilled Dunlending with a bow could kill a veteran warrior with a lucky shot.
Rain of Arrows from the Brockbridge Siege
The perimeter of Brockbridge is crawling with squads of Dunlending archers. They make it very hard for the Rohirrim to make any progress against the siege and should be dealt with.
